OL,6,FA drink driver who killed a passenger
OL,7,Fin a 100mph crash has been jailed.
OL,9,FVideos shared on social media showed
OL,10,Fone of Leon Roberts' passengers saying
OL,11,F"I'm gunna die" before the Mercedes
OL,12,FGLA he was driving collided with a
OL,13,Fparked taxi on Sheffield Parkway in
OL,14,FFebruary 2023.
OL,16,FRoberts, 25, fled the scene, leaving
OL,17,Fhis injured friends fighting for their
OL,18,Flives in a car that was about to burst
OL,19,Finto flames.
