OL,3,CDrink driver who killed passenger in
OL,4,C100mph crash jailed
OL,6,FA male passenger helped others out of
OL,7,Fthe car before emergency services
OL,8,Fattended and took five people to
OL,9,Fhospital, including the taxi driver.
OL,11,FSharna Burgin, 23, was taken to
OL,12,Fintensive care after suffering a
OL,13,F"devastating" brain injury, as well as
OL,14,Frib and spinal fractures. She died in
OL,15,Fhospital.
OL,17,FA surviving passenger later told
OL,18,Fpolice he thought he would die.
