OL,3,CDrink driver who killed passenger in
OL,4,C100mph crash jailed
OL,6,FAfter a 16-hour manhunt, Roberts
OL,7,Fhanded himself in. Tests found he had
OL,8,Ftraces of cocaine, cannabis and
OL,9,Falcohol in his system.
OL,11,FSheffield Crown Court heard how his
OL,12,Fpassengers had begged him to slow down
OL,13,Fand described him as "showing off"
OL,14,Fbefore the crash.
OL,16,FIn a statement given in court, Sharna
OL,17,FBurgin's mother described what had
OL,18,Fhappened as a "nightmare" and said she
OL,19,Fhad been "robbed of a future" with her
OL,20,Fdaughter.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
