OL,3,CDrink driver who killed passenger in
OL,4,C100mph crash jailed
OL,6,FRoberts pleaded guilty to causing
OL,7,Fdeath by dangerous driving and causing
OL,8,Fserious injury by dangerous driving.
OL,10,FHe was jailed for nine years and six
OL,11,Fmonths and disqualified from driving
OL,12,Ffor 14 years and three months.
OL,14,FJudge Jeremy Richardson KC said to
OL,15,FRoberts: "You caused this devastation
OL,16,Fby your arrogance and desire to
OL,17,Fbrazenly show off to your friends.
OL,19,F"You were driving at about 100mph on a
OL,20,Froad where the speed limit was 50mph.
